snippet.title: Drake Reacts FURIOUS To Kim Kardashian Dating Pete Davidson
snippet.description:
Drake Reacts FURIOUS To Kim Kardashian Dating Pete Davidson
If we're being honest with ourselves here, there are only a few times when we are honestly "shook" by something going on in the celeb world. Mainly because after telling so much of what is happening...you'd think we'd have heard it all. But the fact of the matter is that the celebrity world seems to love throwing monkey wrenches into beliefs, and that includes going and putting people together that by no right should be together in a working way. And you know who we're talking about. Yep, it's the latest on the relationship of Kim K and Pete Davidson, and who's reacting to it, we'll break it down for you.
